1 - In the initialize method declare cordinates
    of snake , rows/cols arr and so on.

2 - In the update method prepare enviornment for
    drawing snake game on the screen.This is where
    position of snake will be updated by moving the 
    snake's segments.Generate food and add new segments
    to the snake.

3 - In the draw method take all updated stuff and draw 
    them on the screen.

4 - Update and draw method should be keep running over 
    and over again during the game.